	<h1 class="title">一天吞下40勺糖，会怎样？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Anahad O&#x27; Connor</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-20 07:34:49 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13672/medium/13672.jpg?1439868440" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


